subject: Football

Football (College)
lead_paragraph: Keith Nichol caught a 44-yard desperation heave from Kirk Cousins on the game’s final play for a tiebreaking touchdown, giving No. 15 Michigan State a stunning win over No. 4 Wisconsin.
